  <brief_title>Comparing Fitbit® Quality of Measured Sleep to Sleep Measured by Polysomnography in the Sleep Lab</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparing Fitbit® Quality of Measured Sleep to Sleep Measured by Polysomnography in the Sleep Lab</official_title>
